            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日股今早顯著回升，日經平均指數中午收報57849點，漲1346點或2.38%。</p>\n</div>",
