        {
            "title": "內地首季度出口增長近12%   進口增長近二成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國海關公布，今年一季度出口6.85萬億元(人民幣‧下同)，增長11.9％；進口4.99萬億元，增長19.6％。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Economy.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Economy.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">貨物進出口11.84萬億元，按年增長15%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">首季度中國電動汽車、鋰電池出口分別增長77.5%、50.4%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國對歐盟、英國進出口分別增長14.6%、13.1%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15869802-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e5%ba%a6%e5%87%ba%e5%8f%a3%e5%a2%9e%e9%95%b7%e8%bf%9112-%e9%80%b2%e5%8f%a3%e5%a2%9e%e9%95%b7%e8%bf%91%e4%ba%8c%e6%88%90",
